      <title>比特币涨势在接近历史性 10 万美元水平后停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/bitcoin-s-btc-rally-stalls-after-nearing-the-historic-100-000-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币一度上涨至 10 万美元，但在接近历史水平后回落，随后趋于稳定，交易员正在评估当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对加密货币的支持所带来的乐观情绪是否变得过分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/bitcoin-s-btc-rally-stalls-after-nearing-the-historic-100-000-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 22:00:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
